Comment: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hả?
Comment: 10,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.45,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, her?
Comment: 10,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.66,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's...
Comment: 10,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.58,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\i1}kinda arrogant, don't you think?
Comment: 10,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.13,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I admit she is cute,
Comment: 10,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.83,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she could hang out with him once, at least.
Comment: 10,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.68,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she thinks she's some kind of idol...
Comment: 10,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.64,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Kusakabe?
Comment: 10,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.51,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.99,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 10,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.21,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I-It's just... I heard people...
Comment: 10,0:03:06.21,0:03:10.77,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,s-saying mean things... about me.
Comment: 10,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.05,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 10,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.97,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't the place to talk about it.
Comment: 10,0:03:13.97,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Comment: 10,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.22,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is it because I'm a demi?!
Comment: 10,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,If I weren't a demi,
Comment: 10,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.15,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I wouldn't feel like this...
Comment: 10,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.78,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That's not true.
Comment: 10,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.59,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That isn't true, Kusakabe.
Comment: 10,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.54,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to protect her.
Comment: 10,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to protect this demi{-chan}!
Comment: 10,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.84,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Generally speaking,
Comment: 10,0:03:57.84,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}gossip is a trivial issue, common among high school girls.
Comment: 10,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.12,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But since she's a demi,
Comment: 10,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.56,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}this particular issue isn't quite that simple.
Comment: 10,0:04:09.22,0:04:13.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hikari and Machi have accepted that, and are living normally enough...
Comment: 10,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.32,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ms. Satou?
Comment: 10,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.25,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hydrangeas, eh?
Comment: 10,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.26,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,There were lots of them in the garden,
Comment: 10,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so I borrowed a few.
Comment: 10,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.92,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Are you working, Mr. Takahashi?
Comment: 10,0:04:28.07,0:04:33.15,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yes, with the weather like this, \Nstaying in that dark prep room is depressing.
Comment: 10,0:04:33.15,0:04:37.20,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Um... I was wrong about you, Mr. Takahashi.
Comment: 10,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.55,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,The thing with Machi{-san}'s backpack...
Comment: 10,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.17,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I happened to hear you asking the principal to help.
Comment: 10,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.36,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, that—
Comment: 10,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.88,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Even though you're someone so considerate of demis,
Comment: 10,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.88,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,on the day of the opening ceremony, I behaved that way toward you!
Comment: 10,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.98,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Comment: 10,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.06,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all!
Comment: 10,0:04:55.06,0:04:59.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I should be the one to apologize for being insensitive to your situation.
Comment: 10,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.72,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,As for the backpack, Hikari...
Comment: 10,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.19,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Takanashi asked me to help.
Comment: 10,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.60,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Takanashi{-san}? The older sister, you mean?
Comment: 10,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.32,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 10,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.94,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I work so closely with those girls,
Comment: 10,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.70,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,but I didn't notice anything.
Comment: 10,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.63,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I want to understand them better, but...
Comment: 10,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.80,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Takahashi?
Comment: 10,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.73,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 10,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.06,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 10,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.27,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,C-Can I be of any help at all?
Comment: 10,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.13,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.21,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I'm a demi, after all!
Comment: 10,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.43,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yes, I've experienced that firsthand.
Comment: 10,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.45,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I mean...
Comment: 10,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.53,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,A-And I'm also a teacher!
Comment: 10,0:05:35.53,0:05:39.62,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I have a duty to address the concerns of my demi students!
Comment: 10,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.92,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,With that in mind, I really think I can help!
Comment: 10,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.20,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Oops.
Comment: 10,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.08,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,No, I think that sounds perfect...
Comment: 10,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.30,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate your help.
Comment: 10,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.23,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 10,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.67,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,So, the students who said mean things about Kusakabe...
Comment: 10,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.56,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It seems they constantly gossip about others as well.
Comment: 10,0:06:10.56,0:06:14.05,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Then, Kusakabe{-san} wasn't being specifically targeted?
Comment: 10,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.13,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Comment: 10,0:06:15.13,0:06:19.40,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,But she's convinced that it's because she's a demi?
Comment: 10,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.86,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ms. Satou?
Comment: 10,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.66,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Even without considering the gossip,
Comment: 10,0:06:26.66,0:06:32.21,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Kusakabe{-san} seems to avoid contact with other people, to begin with.
Comment: 10,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.06,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I mean, in a different way than I do.
Comment: 10,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.76,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I noticed that, too.
Comment: 10,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.75,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Maybe she has some reason.
Comment: 10,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.41,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,A reason.
Comment: 10,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.90,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You mean something like her family?
Comment: 10,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.84,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I have a feeling it's more connected to her nature as a demi.
Comment: 10,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.01,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Her nature?
Comment: 10,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.90,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,The reason I had the wrong idea about you
Comment: 10,0:06:52.90,0:06:57.43,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,was because my succubus nature made me overly self-conscious.
Comment: 10,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.57,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I see... There's that way of looking at it.
Comment: 10,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.41,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,She probably doesn't have anyone to talk to about it,
Comment: 10,0:07:03.41,0:07:07.19,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,which makes it even harder to come to terms with her demi identity.
Comment: 10,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.04,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I guess I should have tried to talk to her sooner...
Comment: 10,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.30,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Well, why don't I try to speak to her?
Comment: 10,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.22,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Talking to another demi might be easier for her.
Comment: 10,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.54,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That would be a big help.
Comment: 10,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.69,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'm really glad you're on this with me.
Comment: 10,0:07:24.53,0:07:28.67,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,N-N-N-Not at all! It's just what any teacher ought to do!
Comment: 10,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.26,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Talking to Kusakabe is important...
Comment: 10,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.69,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,But we should also do something about the students who were gossiping.
Comment: 10,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.23,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,You're right.
Comment: 10,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling them to stop won't work.
Comment: 10,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.39,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,They don't want people to know they feel inferior,
Comment: 10,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.66,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,but they're afraid to face their victims.
Comment: 10,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.28,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I believe that mental weakness
Comment: 10,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is what makes people gossip about others.
Comment: 10,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.61,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,If possible,
Comment: 10,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like them to realize that they don't have to rely on gossip.
Comment: 10,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.74,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 10,0:08:00.74,0:08:05.88,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Maybe it would be unfair to expect that from high school students...
Comment: 10,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.41,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Now, what to do?
Comment: 10,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.77,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Takanashi{-san}, wait a minute.
Comment: 10,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.45,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, where are we going?
Comment: 10,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takanashi{-san}...
Comment: 10,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.89,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Takanashi{-san}!
Comment: 10,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hikari?
Comment: 10,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.80,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,{\an8}And they just left it like that.
Comment: 10,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.48,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way! That's crazy!
Comment: 10,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.31,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,{\an8}Also, I heard the physics teacher, Iwai, is being sent to another school.
Comment: 10,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.59,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Takanashi{-san}...
Comment: 10,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.39,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yukki, I'm going to give them a piece of my mind.
Comment: 10,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.43,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really? Why?
Comment: 10,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.79,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You wait here and listen.
Comment: 10,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.79,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,{\an8}It seems like he got involved in some risky stuff.
Comment: 10,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.39,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\an8}What the hell?
Comment: 10,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.08,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'll let you decide what happens afterward.
Comment: 10,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.31,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,{\an8}With that face, maybe it can't be helped.
Comment: 10,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.04,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,{\an8}You think he went after someone?
Comment: 10,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.71,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,No way. He wouldn't have the guts.
Comment: 10,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.75,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,What a loser!
Comment: 10,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.05,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Aren't you from class B?
Comment: 10,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.06,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Oh, the vampire.
Comment: 10,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.01,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Takanashi...
Comment: 10,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.48,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Is trashing people behind their backs all you ever do?
Comment: 10,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.60,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Comment: 10,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.75,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.57,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Oh, is this about Kusakabe?
Comment: 10,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.97,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,As a fellow demi, you're out to avenge her?
Comment: 10,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cool of—
Comment: 10,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.57,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.03,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yes, Yukki is a demi, but it doesn't matter!
Comment: 10,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.77,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'm giving you two a piece of my mind
Comment: 10,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's what I want to do!
Comment: 10,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.62,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Don't try to dodge it by provoking me!
Comment: 10,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.43,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,If you don't want to stop blabbing about people, then fine...
Comment: 10,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.13,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,But every time I see or hear you doing it,
Comment: 10,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.21,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'll call you on it.
Comment: 10,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.84,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,If you want to hang around and badmouth people,
Comment: 10,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.38,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,you'd better do it where I can't find you.
Comment: 10,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.02,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.96,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,We aren't the only ones who talk about people behind their backs.
Comment: 10,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.42,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Why single us out?
Comment: 10,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.08,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It won't be just you two.
Comment: 10,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.07,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'll give a piece of my mind to anyone I catch badmouthing someone else!
Comment: 10,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.37,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Why are you so gung-ho about this?
Comment: 10,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.90,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Everyone talks about people behind their backs.
Comment: 10,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.75,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I can't stand the excuse that "everyone does it"!
Comment: 10,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.14,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Everyone hurts people,
Comment: 10,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so you think you're allowed to hurt people?
Comment: 10,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.75,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed to say that?
Comment: 10,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.87,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No one in the world likes being badmouthed!
Comment: 10,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.15,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,What, so you never talk about anyone behind their back?
Comment: 10,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.40,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No. If I want to say something, I say it to their face.
Comment: 10,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.70,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,If I can't, I say nothing.
Comment: 10,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.06,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You think that will keep people from talking about you?
Comment: 10,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.50,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Comment: 10,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.45,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I know as soon as I leave,
Comment: 10,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.39,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,you two will start griping about me.
Comment: 10,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.85,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 10,0:10:27.60,0:10:31.33,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It was mean of me to say it that way.
Comment: 10,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.57,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Huh? Er, s-sure...
Comment: 10,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.89,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I know people who don't badmouth others still get badmouthed.
Comment: 10,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.44,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,In fact, they're probably the easiest targets.
Comment: 10,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.24,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,But I've made up my mind!
Comment: 10,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.64,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It's just for my satisfaction, but...
Comment: 10,0:10:45.09,0:10:49.54,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Even if people say mean things about me, I won't do anything I'll regret!
Comment: 10,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.15,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Are you... crying?
Comment: 10,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.15,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Sorry, I've said what I wanted to say.
Comment: 10,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.42,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'll go now.
Comment: 10,0:11:01.92,0:11:04.95,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,I can't agree with what you said,
Comment: 10,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.14,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,but I am kinda impressed.
Comment: 10,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.94,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Still, why would you say all that?
Comment: 10,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.77,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Because I promised...
Comment: 10,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.53,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I promised my sister.
Comment: 10,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.28,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Your sister?
Comment: 10,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.72,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hima—
Comment: 10,0:11:33.21,0:11:33.88,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Ku...
Comment: 10,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.23,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Kusakabe...
Comment: 10,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.21,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Comment: 10,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.09,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I, um...
Comment: 10,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.48,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,The truth is, my demi nature still bothers me,
Comment: 10,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.59,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,so I've always avoided contact with people.
Comment: 10,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.10,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,If that gave you a bad impression,
Comment: 10,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,well... I'm sorry.
Comment: 10,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.58,Default,Kimura,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Comment: 10,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.03,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,We're the ones who should...
Comment: 10,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.03,Default,Imori,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 10,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.68,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Wha—
Comment: 10,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.10,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,The rain stopped.
Comment: 10,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.92,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You—
Comment: 10,0:12:13.24,0:12:16.20,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You hungry? I'll treat you to something.
Comment: 10,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.22,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Comment: 10,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.30,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It hurts when you rub my head where my hair's tied up!
Comment: 10,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.61,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Comment: 10,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.67,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,If you're gonna rub it, rub the back!
Comment: 10,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.15,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Comment: 10,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.79,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Comment: 10,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.65,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.69,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Don't ask.
Comment: 10,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.65,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd this come from?
Comment: 10,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.69,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Don't ask.
Comment: 10,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.66,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Did something happen at school?
Comment: 10,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.42,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Comment: 10,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.88,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,The thing is, a student came to talk to me recently...
Comment: 10,0:12:53.88,0:12:58.05,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I had my own thoughts about it, so I called you all here.
Comment: 10,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.25,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ms. Satou, too.
Comment: 10,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.48,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Someone talked to you? It wasn't me.
Comment: 10,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.36,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Me, either.
Comment: 10,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.75,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Can't you guys be more sensitive?
Comment: 10,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.77,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Comment: 10,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.70,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,W-We couldn't help it! There's only three of us here!
Comment: 10,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.70,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Anyway, I know there are many things demis might worry about now.
Comment: 10,0:13:17.70,0:13:22.03,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'd like for you three to be able to help each other out.
Comment: 10,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.62,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You three are the only demi students at this school.
Comment: 10,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.07,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'd like you to treasure that link among you.
Comment: 10,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.79,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,If you can't confide in your friends, you can come to me or Ms. Satou.
Comment: 10,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.08,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,In particular, Ms. Satou, is a demi, like you, as well as a woman.
Comment: 10,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.13,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,There's no one you can trust more.
Comment: 10,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.75,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I'd rather be the one seeking advice from—
Comment: 10,0:13:41.60,0:13:44.74,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,F-Feel free to talk to me anytime, too!
Comment: 10,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.86,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to say.
Comment: 10,0:13:46.86,0:13:53.56,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I hope you're aware that getting together to discuss things like this is important.
Comment: 10,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.96,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Does anyone have anything they'd like to talk about right now?
Comment: 10,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.84,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I guess you can't think of anything right now.
Comment: 10,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.32,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That'll be all for today, then—
Comment: 10,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.14,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Me!
Comment: 10,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.82,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I haven't gotten a hug from you yet!
Comment: 10,0:14:07.31,0:14:07.66,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.07,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Hug?
Comment: 10,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.83,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Comment: 10,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.44,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Squeeze...
Comment: 10,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.80,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hee hee.
Comment: 10,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.25,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ha ha... What?
Comment: 10,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.60,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hee hee hee!
Comment: 10,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.46,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha. Seriously, what?
Comment: 10,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.05,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,C-Can I have one, too?
Comment: 10,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.59,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:14:25.02,0:14:25.76,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Sure.
Comment: 10,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.45,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 10,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.41,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,No problem.
Comment: 10,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.20,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Good for you, Macchi!
Comment: 10,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.26,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Yep.
Comment: 10,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.72,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.19,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,I'll take one, too—
Comment: 10,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.78,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,No, that's a bad idea...
Comment: 10,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.27,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,You're right.
Comment: 10,0:14:49.30,0:14:49.91,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Uh...
Comment: 10,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.49,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,How about it, Kusakabe? If you'd like one, too...
Comment: 10,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.55,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,While we're at it.
Comment: 10,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.42,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.59,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,While you're at it?!
Comment: 10,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.08,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Kusakabe...
Comment: 10,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.46,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I won't force you to talk about what's troubling you.
Comment: 10,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.43,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Like I said before,
Comment: 10,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's fate that you're in an environment
Comment: 10,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.93,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,where you're surrounded by other demis.
Comment: 10,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.41,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,So... I can't say it well, but I'm sure it'll get better.
Comment: 10,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.06,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You will have fun.
Comment: 10,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.11,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Comment: 10,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.54,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Okay?
Comment: 10,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.73,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 10,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.45,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Mr. T, Mr. T!
Comment: 10,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.62,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Give her a hug, too!
Comment: 10,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.36,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Her? But that's Machi.
Comment: 10,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.15,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Just while you're at it!
Comment: 10,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.55,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Sheesh... Is that all right, Machi?
Comment: 10,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.58,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Comment: 10,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.13,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Comment: 10,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.57,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, that'll be all for today.
Comment: 10,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.76,Default,Sakie,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi, what was that weird scream?!
Comment: 10,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.93,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What happened?
Comment: 10,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.34,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Wait! I have a question!
Comment: 10,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what that reaction meant!
Comment: 10,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.96,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,He called all the demis together for a meeting?
Comment: 10,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.48,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, Mr. Takahashi had them meet in the AV room after classes.
Comment: 10,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.99,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi did?
Comment: 10,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Hikari{-chan} said it was a lot of fun.
Comment: 10,0:16:13.66,0:16:17.98,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,He seems pretty spacey, but he's actually very caring.
Comment: 10,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.17,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Comment: 10,0:16:19.17,0:16:19.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 10,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.54,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Comment: 10,0:16:24.41,0:16:28.38,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}To tell the truth, I still don't trust Mr. Takahashi!
Comment: 10,0:16:29.74,0:16:33.03,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I got careless since it was just her body, and I hugged too hard.
Comment: 10,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I wonder if Machi noticed.
Comment: 10,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.05,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course she did...
Comment: 10,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.18,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 10,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.60,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Hello.
Comment: 10,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.02,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,I didn't know teachers were allowed to leave so early.
Comment: 10,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.04,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Comment: 10,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.85,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,And I see you stayed pretty late, Himari{-chan}.
Comment: 10,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.20,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,I did. I like the library.
Comment: 10,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.66,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I hear you did amazingly well on the last exams.
Comment: 10,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.02,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Comment: 10,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.76,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You always study in the library?
Comment: 10,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.39,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, and I read books to refresh myself.
Comment: 10,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.17,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 10,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.50,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You're nothing like Hikari, huh?
Comment: 10,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.47,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was suspicious.
Comment: 10,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.46,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always nice to my sister, but...
Comment: 10,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.34,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 10,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.55,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,N-Nothing...
Comment: 10,0:17:17.01,0:17:20.31,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Just worried that my sister's been bothering you.
Comment: 10,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I've been letting her cool off in the Phòng Sinh Học.
Comment: 10,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.39,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that right?
Comment: 10,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or are you actually looking at her as an experimental sample?
Comment: 10,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, the experiment.
Comment: 10,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.28,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I forgot to prepare one for tomorrow's class.
Comment: 10,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I hope I'll have enough materials for everyone.
Comment: 10,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, I can do it tomorrow.
Comment: 10,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.88,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm overthinking this...
Comment: 10,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.20,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if he does love demis,
Comment: 10,0:17:38.20,0:17:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's no way he thinks about the nature of vampires around the clock.
Comment: 10,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.48,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, right!
Comment: 10,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you something about the nature of vampires.
Comment: 10,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.25,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}He actually does!
Comment: 10,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.00,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Wh-What would that be?
Comment: 10,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.23,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hikari seems to have no problem chowing down on garlic,
Comment: 10,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.64,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,but the stories you hear assume that vampires hate garlic.
Comment: 10,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.56,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I was thinking about whether it was all fake.
Comment: 10,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.40,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Comment: 10,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.69,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,They say vampires attack humans at night, under cover of darkness.
Comment: 10,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.71,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Comment: 10,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.66,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Uh, isn't it because they hate sunlight?
Comment: 10,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.15,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I don't think that makes them scary enough for people to carry crosses.
Comment: 10,0:18:10.15,0:18:14.42,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Some books say that vampires have very keen senses.
Comment: 10,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.24,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I think that's the reason.
Comment: 10,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.24,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Sharp vision, even at night, hearing that can detect humans,
Comment: 10,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.47,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,a sharp sense of smell to pick up the scent of blood.
Comment: 10,0:18:22.47,0:18:26.42,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That's more than enough for an advantage over humans in the dark.
Comment: 10,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.61,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,What does the sharpness of their senses have to do with garlic?
Comment: 10,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.14,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, the key point is their sense of smell.
Comment: 10,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.84,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Since their noses are so sensitive, they hate strong-smelling foods.
Comment: 10,0:18:35.84,0:18:40.46,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I think that's why vampires in legends hate garlic.
Comment: 10,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.49,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about those things, but what's the real story?
Comment: 10,0:18:43.49,0:18:46.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Does Hikari have sharp senses?
Comment: 10,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.73,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Yes, that's quite accurate.
Comment: 10,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.58,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,My sister's senses are incredible.
Comment: 10,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.06,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh! All right!
Comment: 10,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.38,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Then, how can she eat so much garlic?
Comment: 10,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.28,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,That's because...
Comment: 10,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.13,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,She just isn't picky enough about her food.
Comment: 10,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.32,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,I got concerned and asked her if she was forcing herself to eat it.
Comment: 10,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.16,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,And she said...
Comment: 10,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.98,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!
Comment: 10,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.04,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I love foods that smell really strong!
Comment: 10,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.39,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want her to say that in public.
Comment: 10,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.80,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,You can say that again...
Comment: 10,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.91,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Lots of people who talk to me about my sister say
Comment: 10,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.02,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,she doesn't seem like a vampire,
Comment: 10,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.43,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,that she's just like a normal high school girl.
Comment: 10,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.85,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,You seem very interested in demis' natures,
Comment: 10,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.31,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,so what do you think of that?
Comment: 10,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.48,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Do you think my sister doesn't seem like a vampire?!
Comment: 10,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.32,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Are you not that interested in her human side?
Comment: 10,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.79,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give you a straight answer.
Comment: 10,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.86,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It's true that she doesn't behave the way I'd expect a vampire to.
Comment: 10,0:19:47.86,0:19:50.60,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,But if you asked whether that makes her unlike a vampire,
Comment: 10,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.96,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'd say it doesn't.
Comment: 10,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.92,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hikari does want to suck people's blood,
Comment: 10,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.17,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,but she settles for blood bags.
Comment: 10,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.67,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,And even though she has a vampire's keen sense of smell,
Comment: 10,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.03,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,she loves foods with strong scents.
Comment: 10,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.82,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That human side is what makes her like a vampire,
Comment: 10,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.43,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,and it's what makes her unique.
Comment: 10,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.42,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It isn't how you're born that makes you "like" something.
Comment: 10,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.31,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It's how you live with what you are.
Comment: 10,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.61,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean it's okay to ignore a demi's nature.
Comment: 10,0:20:18.61,0:20:23.11,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,The concerns unique to demis are caused by their natures.
Comment: 10,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.12,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You can't look at things in only one way.
Comment: 10,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.58,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You should look from both angles.
Comment: 10,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.33,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,If you just see traits unique to demis, you'll miss their individuality.
Comment: 10,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.53,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,If you only see the human side, you won't understand their troubles.
Comment: 10,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Both are precious.
Comment: 10,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.59,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What's important is balance.
Comment: 10,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.46,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Comment: 10,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.47,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm speechless.
Comment: 10,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.14,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I can trust him...
Comment: 10,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.71,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.02,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What's up?
Comment: 10,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.74,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to our house sometime?
Comment: 10,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.73,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, I did, not long ago.
Comment: 10,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of it, anyway.
Comment: 10,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.94,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,I'd like my parents to hear what you just said.
Comment: 10,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.98,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Comment: 10,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.74,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Actually, I was thinking I'd like to talk to your parents, too.
Comment: 10,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.92,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi...
Comment: 10,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Comment: 10,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.45,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,By the way, I have a question for you!
Comment: 10,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.23,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,What does hugging my sister let you learn?
Comment: 10,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.29,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Was it her vampire nature, or her human side?!
Comment: 10,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.74,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hugged? Attacked?!
Comment: 10,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking?
Comment: 10,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong, Himari{-chan}! She's the one who—
Comment: 10,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.22,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,You...
Comment: 10,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.26,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Rationalizing, demi-loving teacher!
Comment: 10,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.35,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I don't deny that, but still!
Comment: 10,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.69,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Sis?
Comment: 10,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.83,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Sister, are you oka—
Comment: 10,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.73,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,And why send me such a misleading message?
Comment: 10,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.32,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Comment: 10,0:21:41.32,0:21:45.26,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You were so late getting home, and I was bored here.
Comment: 10,0:21:45.26,0:21:49.68,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I thought if I sent a message like that, you'd come home faster.
Comment: 10,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.41,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I had no idea Mr. T was with you.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.89,0:21:58.42,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,If you'd just sent a message asking me to hurry home, I would have.
Comment: 10,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.29,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Really? I love you, Himari!
Comment: 10,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.63,Default,Himari,0,0,0,,Quit clinging to me!
Comment: 10,0:22:04.97,0:22:04.97,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
